Package: cuda12.8
Title: CUDA 12.8 Toolkit Libraries
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R:
    person("Daniel", "Falbel", , "daniel@posit.co", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides CUDA 12.8 native libraries (runtime, cuBLAS, cuDNN, cuFFT,
    cuSOLVER, cuSPARSE, CUPTI, NVRTC, NvJitLink, NCCL, NVSHMEM, and NVCC) by
    downloading pre-built binaries from PyPI. Intended to be used as a dependency
    by packages that require CUDA 12.8.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/dfalbel/cudatoolkit
BugReports: https://github.com/dfalbel/cudatoolkit/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
